### Summary
Update of serialization packages `holochain-serialization` and `holochain-wasmer-*` leads to general message format change for enums. Previously an enum value like
```rust
enum Enum {
  Variant1,
  Variant2,
}
let value = Enum::Variant1;
```
was serialized as (JSON representation)
```json
{
  "value": {
    "variant1": null
  }
}
```
Now it serializes to
```json
{
  "value": "variant1"
}
```

related to #3598 

